{"tid":1611346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：對暴徒極端暴力行為表示極度憤慨","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T03:07:22.000Z","uid":38954,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"de3c01b91876d8692f03b74ac1d8ce8c2f3ff9ce","tid":1611346,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府對星期二在多區爆發的衝突表示極度憤慨，認為有關行為威脅市民安全以及破壞社會秩序，社會應予以最強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n政府形容星期二多區爆發的衝突為暴徒的極端暴力行為，對此表示極度憤慨，認為暴力行為對市民安全構成極大威脅，嚴重破壞社會秩序，社會應予以最強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，為保障市民安全和恢復社會秩序，警務人員有必要採取適當武力作驅散和拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n政府又指多區出現暴動，是有組織、有計劃的破壞，令香港陷入混亂和恐慌，反映事件已經變質，而社會不希望學生受煽動而犯法，呼籲家長和老師應勸喻子女和學生，切勿參與未經批准的集會及遊行活動。"},{"pid":"48ea00b58562499fffa034628682e79095f66c95","tid":1611346,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"71ddf239faf62d318cb2790aaf7798bd921f54e4","tid":1611346,"uid":47208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"由6月到而家都係呢d字眼"},{"pid":"9ff597bf0a9762ced2a1a6cda03de1e54c51982f","tid":1611346,"uid":73915,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"十月一日都唔敢講<br />\n星期二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fdaa878cd2f6455bae3ccce8e3194b01f73c4c","tid":1611346,"uid":13308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:44:35.000Z","msg":"比d新意好無"},{"pid":"2313fba130d500e6218d8c5eda0833a06a9fffa5","tid":1611346,"uid":35818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/TidyFluidCuckoo-size